Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:09.40,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:12.40,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:40.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:42.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shiina, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:43.83,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:50.20,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A person must first experience \Npain to be able to pilot Nyapollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:51.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:56.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I will defeat all of the Nyangoro aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:01:00.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to respond \Nto that kind of confession...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:02.09,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Shiina, h-hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.58,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:07.76,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're being a wimp, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:08.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:12.71,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Take your rejection like a man,\N for the sake of Earth's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:28.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.91,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(792,1)}#13 One Step Before Winter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What was with that dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.30,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you still dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san? What are you, psychic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.93,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I get that a lot, but I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:28.61,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might still be buzzing\N from the Nyapollon experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:38.61,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Culture Festival Multiplayer Game:{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:38.61,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Please participate in the following survey about "Milky Way Cat Nyapollon."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon's survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.65,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,This is the majority of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.61,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everyone enjoyed the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.64,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It was because everyone else \Ndid such a great job...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:49.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't matter who was in my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.29,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The end result would \Nhave been the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.67,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's very modest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:55.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a level-headed analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:56.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel a little more confident now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.30,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to reapply to the \N"Let's Make a Game!" contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I submitted my \Napplication right after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.48,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:14.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Akasaka told me to look over the notes \Nfrom the Nyapollon review meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.62,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so that I wouldn't make\N the same mistakes again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,and I wrote a pitch based on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.69,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,So, how confident are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.10,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:26.22,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,Your entry has been submitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.16,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Ryunosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:33.84,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty bold of Rita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:37.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's been texting me \Nconstantly since that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.34,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I finally gave her Akasaka's number.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.21,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Maid-chan must have been mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:43.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Completely outraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:47.66,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if those two could \Nget it together properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.44,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro asked me if I knew \Nwhere Kanda-kun was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you might be \Nup here, so I brought her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.49,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:03.03,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You came looking for me because \Nyou needed something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.26,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:16.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I found everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.25,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.09,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do, kouhai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:24.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My once-in-a-lifetime \Nopportunity has presented itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what \Nyou're talking—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:38.23,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you pouncing me \Nthis early in the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.85,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wait until tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:43.57,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm in danger, \Nso I'll be staying out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Jin, I made you lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.71,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:52.12,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Jin-san just eating bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.28,Sign,FOOD,0000,0000,0000,,I Love You
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.02,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did it win your stomach over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:04.84,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't eaten any yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:07.80,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.16,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see something you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.07,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What did Shiina come up here to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:17.88,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:21.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.98,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it even more gorgeous next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.44,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand Mashiro, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:29.58,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to tomorrow's lunch, Jin! Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I do, but I'm not telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:32.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:36.16,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not {\i1}that{\i0} nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:41.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, you{\i1} are{\i0} kinda mean \Nto me sometimes, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.78,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:55.26,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm depressed. Christmas is next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:56.61,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:59.42,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you saying \Nyou have plans, Yayoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:02.25,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm throwing a party for the Softball Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:04.53,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.67,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have plans, Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.40,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.59,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kanda? \NWhat will you do about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,"Do"? What do you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.65,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know that people suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.75,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun and Shiina-san are dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.75,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to get your act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:21.17,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's not fair to Miyahara, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But I turned him down...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! How do you know about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:28.27,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious just by looking at Miyahara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.26,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:32.01,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you've got \Nto make your intentions clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:32.88,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.60,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,To: Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:46.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mitaka-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aoyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.37,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.09,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Wedding Registration
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:58.04,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.04,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiigusa Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:02.87,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,C-Congratulations on getting hitched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:06.04,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny, Aoyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.03,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised \NKamiigusa-senpai sent you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.75,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.84,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something I've \Nbeen meaning to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:13.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.89,Sign,TICKETS,0000,0000,0000,,Happy White Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.89,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, why don't you \Ngo see this with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:20.14,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Tickets to a play! Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.73,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Asami-san invited me, \Nbut she can't make it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:27.33,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be wrong of me to invite someone \Nelse, so you can have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.40,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I almost forgot:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.16,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The performance is on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:33.99,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.65,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to use the tools at your disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:43.00,Sign,TICKETS,0000,0000,0000,,Happy White Christmas\NDec. 24, 7:00 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:55.80,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,what were you going to \Ndo if I had taken off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,my underwear while I was changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.32,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I would have knocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be too late by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to say you \Ndon't need anything again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:07.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,No, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:11.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Promise you won't get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're telling me that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.61,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you must be about to \Nsay something crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:15.89,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredibly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, don't lead off with \Na weird statement like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:21.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make a lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.33,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make a lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Shiina. A lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, don't grab my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:35.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Heed my words, Shiina. \NGreat potential lies within all humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,However, there are some \Nthings people cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,People cannot grow wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,These are things you have to accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.40,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,There! That should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san, why are you \Nputting an apron on her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:47.81,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look, Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:48.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.65,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I never dreamed you'd be so forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:53.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:56.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina and cooking seriously don't mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:58.16,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:00.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It looks to me like you're \Nready to make {\i1}me{\i0} cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:03.37,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to go meet Rumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.66,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Jin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:11.57,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata... I... cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:15.30,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need to work on your manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:21.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You must be behind schedule \Nbecause of the culture festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:22.72,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.87,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work on my manuscript later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do it later?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:28.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:29.97,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:34.53,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to teach you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.03,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Your main dish will be fried mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll also make fried eggs and a salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:52.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.42,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to repeat what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Crack the egg by hitting it \Nagainst a bowl like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.51,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and then, break it in \Nhalf with both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:03.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.80,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Break it in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like a parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:17.81,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who's just sent their kid out on \Nan errand for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.40,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, where's the knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No. Only after you've \Nleveled up your cooking skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:23.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I can break eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:26.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I like knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much do you like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.03,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,So much that I can't sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:32.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I hear ya. Let's use a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you hold it \Nwhen attacking someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.27,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,This way feels more natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.27,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't point it at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:42.03,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you planning to cook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be cooked?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:45.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You can't cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No more knives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.18,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, hold it normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:54.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Fold the fingers of your free \Nhand when you use a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:56.56,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Like a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you do, don't cut yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? The end—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:09.08,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Did I win your stomach over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:11.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all it takes to win my stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:16.17,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be the guy who was won \Nover by a cucumber farmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.33,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking's so deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What could you possibly have understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.55,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,just by cutting off the end of a cucumber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut some more, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Fold your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.83,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Like a cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:31.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You klutz, let me see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Shii—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:43.11,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There, that should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.04,Saku-main,CHIHARU,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm s-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:56.37,Saku-main,CHIHARU,0000,0000,0000,,What are you apologizing for? It's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.03,Saku-main,CHIHARU,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able to finish your manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.67,Saku-main,CHIHARU,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the deadline tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I have the cover left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.57,Saku-main,CHIHARU,0000,0000,0000,,You should contact your editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:16.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:20.34,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, don't you want me to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to injure yourself \Nany more than you did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.36,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's not it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.07,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:31.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Enough talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's her problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.22,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Up until recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:59.23,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Up until recently, it seemed like \Nshe lived solely to draw manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:05.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.36,Saku-main,YUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I want you for my \NChristmas present, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you want to speak to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.16,Saku-main,YUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.15,Saku-main,YUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:17.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want something, Yuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.67,Saku-main,YUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan?! I just had a \Nsupernatural experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.81,Saku-main,YUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I called the number in my contacts list,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:23.68,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it connected me to someone—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what you call a \N"supernatural experience."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.84,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.81,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I like brown foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:39.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Will her manuscript be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.47,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,From the looks of it, \Nshe'll finish up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:45.42,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,The cut on her finger doesn't \Nseem to be causing any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:52.01,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to give me \Nyour honest opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:54.18,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about \NShiina-san now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:54.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.78,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, has she gotten prettier or cuter,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:59.06,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,or do you get the urge to hold her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you trying to get me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.70,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Putting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting it aside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.21,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Shiina-san has \Nchanged a little lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:11.74,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met her, \Nshe had the face of an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:16.03,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,A strange feeling washed \Nover me while talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.78,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,She was looking at me\N with those lucid eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but not really seeing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.94,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed otherworldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:29.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I got the same feeling the \Nfirst time I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.61,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,It's different now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.12,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make a lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.91,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work on my manuscript later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:40.46,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:46.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at Shiina now, \Nsomething feels off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's something uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Or unpleasant... No, that's not it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:55.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It just... well, it irritates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.35,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,That's a valuable opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Before, it seemed like the \Nonly thing she thought about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:03.18,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,was manga, and nothing else mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:05.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But then she suddenly \Nsays she wants to cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.92,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the current Shiina isn't\N the real Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:16.31,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I actually think her current \Nbehavior is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.32,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Normal for a girl, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.75,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm conflicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:28.40,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,It's important for a girl who's\N spent her whole life studying art...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to have normal high school experiences...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:33.92,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and learn what it means to be normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:40.79,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,But if that causes her to lose her \Nunique outlook on the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:47.19,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about things \Nan editor shouldn't worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:52.37,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Her talents and experiences \Nwon't falter on her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.44,Saku-main,SORTA,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda understand what you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:55.99,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Before, or now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.74,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, which is the Shiina-san you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:06.08,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,But in this case, if you choose either \Nanswer, it means you like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:07.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel more at ease around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the old Shiina than the new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:23.23,Sign,MAIL,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda Sorata-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.50,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:45.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:46.94,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What about your manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.34,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:55.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt yourself doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:57.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What if you hurt yourself \Nagain and it doesn't heal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,within a day or two next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:01.84,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:02.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on your manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:07.64,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I finished my manuscript...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You used to work harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You focused on raising the \Nquality as much as you could!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:17.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,People who have been allowed \Nto draw shouldn't slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.42,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:31.29,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, get out from inside of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.05,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.47,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what this feeling is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.39,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.66,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,End-of-Year Party Announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:00.99,Saku-thought,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a little early, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.56,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,the publisher's having an end-of-year party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:06.20,Saku-thought,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to give it to Shiina-san, \Nso could you give it to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I missed the right timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:21.97,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, I need your \Nadvice about something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:24.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you Santa in a miniskirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.04,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Only a few more nights until Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:27.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's still more than a month away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.18,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Want a lift?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:38.95,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,He might already have \Nplans for Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.53,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's hard to invite him \Nwhen we're not even dating...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.53,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:46.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:50.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai wanted my \Nadvice about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know. Come in\N with me, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,How can I make my feelings reach Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:59.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't dressed like \Nsomeone who's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.18,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending out such passionate signals,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.68,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but Jin's too dense to notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So, these passionate feelings \Nyou're trying to send him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.88,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You know I wrote "I love \Nyou" on his lunch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:12.26,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I even put a marriage registration \Nform in his shoe locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:13.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marriage registration?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,And when I took him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,around the back of the school \Nand confessed my feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.69,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,all he said was: "It's cold. \NLet's go back inside."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.82,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,And when I confessed my \Nfeelings behind the gym,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:25.95,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,all he said was: "I'm tired. \NLet's go home."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely ignoring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:28.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:32.92,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've done everything I can, \Nbut he thinks it's all a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:37.80,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've decided to \Nresort to my final option.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Your final option?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:42.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,On Christmas Eve, I want you to \Nleave me alone with Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:43.80,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.22,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She had her answer before she \Neven asked for my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:51.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:52.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.37,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:54.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:58.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go... to your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:09.16,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:11.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:12.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:15.89,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I have two tickets to a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:19.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you'd go with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:20.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A play?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:24.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's actually on Christmas Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:24.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:26.60,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? I-It's on the 24th.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:28.55,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want \Nto make plans with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure everyone else \Nhas plans, so why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:32.94,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:33.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:34.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:37.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you really don't trust me, \Nwe can pinky swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:37.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I was only kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:42.83,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:34.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I anxious on Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:40.98,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,1)}#14 The Windows and Lights of Christmas Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be my first time spending \NChristmas with a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:38.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is a big step up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:40.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should recite some \Nsutras to calm down...
